				<span class="cat-links"><i class="fas fa-book"></i><a href="http://www.antoniocaramia.it/index.php/category/articoli/" rel="category tag">Articoli</a></span><span class="posted-on"><i class="far fa-calendar-alt"></i><a href="http://www.antoniocaramia.it/index.php/2020/08/15/antonio-caramia-tra-surrealismo-magico-e-letteratura-in-memoria-di-gianni-rodardi/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2020-08-15T16:44:00+02:00">15 Agosto 2020</time><time class="updated" datetime="2020-10-06T16:49:36+02:00">6 Ottobre 2020</time></a></span><span class="byline"><i class="fas fa-feather-alt"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.antoniocaramia.it/index.php/author/antonio/">Antonio Caramia</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
				
	</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
